      "type": "html",
      "text": "\nAll writing here is a gift to the community, as is the editing that a few visitors provide. [[Thread Mode]] provides a convenience to those who visit regularly at the expense of the many more occasional readers. I encourage the more even-handed thread participants to eventually tighten up every page so that important ideas are expressed clearly and concisely, at the possible expense of ego. -- [[Ward Cunningham]] [<i>Ditto. -- Anonymous, [[Tim Chambers]]</i>]",
      "id": "120f3b6210aa13a27b1d178c7ee3ffbe"
